This is quite possibly the best video ever.  I love it.  The dad is so strong and handsome. Make it on DVD!

My 4 year old boy and 2 year old girl are in love with this video!!!  They dance, move, and sing the whole time! I love that they are active and learning songs and bible verses at the same time!!! It's old-school cheesy at times, but they love it so much!!! :-)
